SenangSync — Project Brief

 1. Problem Statement


"Your business is everywhere. SenangSync puts it in one place."



Malaysian SME owners waste hours every week hunting for business documents, links, subscriptions, and product info scattered across WhatsApp, Google Drive, Notes, and Canva — SenangSync puts everything in one place so you can find anything in seconds.

The Pain Points


Brand kit stored in Canva, nowhere else
Important docs (SSM, bank statements, certs) scattered across Google Drive folders
Subscription list tracked in WhatsApp notes or phone Notes app
Business links (website, payment form, Google Form, sales page) saved everywhere
Product prices and sales links have no single source of truth



2. What Is SenangSync?

SenangSync is a Business Operating System (Business OS) built specifically for Malaysian SME founders, freelancers, and creative consultants. It is a centralized workspace where everything a business needs to operate — documents, links, subscriptions, and products — lives in one place.

Think of it as "Google for your business" — you open it, you search, you get the thing.

Target Users


Malaysian SME founders and solopreneurs
Creative agency owners and consultants
Digital product sellers (courses, templates, SaaS)
Freelancers managing multiple clients and subscriptions



