6. Design System

6.1 Design Philosophy


Local first — feels made for Malaysians, not translated for them
Fast retrieval — every interaction optimised for finding things quickly
Mobile first — design for phone screen first, scale up to desktop
Clean, not generic — avoid default Shadcn/v0 AI-generated aesthetic
Kedai runcit test — if a 35-year-old Malay SME owner in Klang opened this, they should feel it was built for them


6.2 Typography


Heading: Plus Jakarta Sans (600, 700)
Body: Plus Jakarta Sans (400, 500)
Avoid Inter — too overused in AI-generated UI


6.3 Theme System

Default Theme — Malaysia

The default theme on first load uses the main Malaysian flag colors. Every new user starts here before choosing a state theme.

