6.4 Folder Color Logic


Folders auto-assigned colors from active theme palette (rotating order)
No two adjacent folders share the same color
User can manually override color when editing a folder
Gradient style: single color, lighter shade at top → solid at bottom
Text on dark folders: white. Text on yellow/gold folders: dark brown


6.5 Icon Strategy


Use animated icons from pqoqubbw/icons

GitHub: https://github.com/pqoqubbw/icons
Live preview: https://lucide-animated.com



Built with Framer Motion — subtle, smooth animations on hover/interaction
Icon color follows active theme primary color (same as TNG eWallet approach)
Icons tinted to brand/flag color, not plain black
Sidebar navigation: use the same animated icon set for consistency


6.6 Language Toggle


BM / BI toggle lives directly on the Dashboard — accessible at all times, no need to go into Settings
BM is the default language
Toggle persists per user session (saved to user preferences in Supabase)
BM copy: natural, conversational ("Folder baru", "Semua clear!", "Jom tambah!")
BI copy: clean professional English
Empty states are encouraging and contextual — not generic "No data found"
Toast messages have personality ("Copied! Senang kan?" / "Copied! Easy right?")



