8. Key Principles for Rebuild


Depth over breadth — 3 core modules done perfectly beats 6 done averagely
Retrieval speed is the product — everything optimised for finding things fast
Mobile first — design for phone, enhance for desktop; Malaysian SMEs live on their phones
Local by default — BM as default language, MYR as default currency, Malaysia flag as default theme
Command Bar everywhere — Cmd+K available on every page, not just Dashboard
Auto-assign, allow override — reduce friction on creation, allow customisation later
Language toggle on Dashboard — always one tap away, never buried in settings



